'''旋齒鯊'''（{{lang-en|Helicoprion}}）是一种已[[滅絕|滅絕]]形似[[鯊魚|鯊魚]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://science.nbcnews.com/_news/2013/02/27/17118881-ancient-shark-relative-had-buzzsaw-mouth?lite|title=Ancient shark relative had buzzsaw mouth|first=|last=|date=|website=nbcnews.com|accessdate=2019-01-03|archive-date=2017-10-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171011073244/http://science.nbcnews.com/_news/2013/02/27/17118881-ancient-shark-relative-had-buzzsaw-mouth?lite|dead-url=yes}}</ref>的[[全頭亞綱|全頭亞綱]]魚類，首次出現2.9億年前[[二疊紀|二疊紀]]早期<ref>[http://paleobiology.si.edu/helicoprion/ Page at Smithsonian National Museum of Natural History] {{Wayback|url=http://paleobiology.si.edu/helicoprion/ |date=20180618230522 }}<!-- NO SOURCE FOUND FOR CARBONIFEROUS!!!--></ref>約{{Ma|290}}，在[[二叠纪－三叠纪灭绝事件|二叠纪－三叠纪灭绝事件]]倖存，最終2.5億年前的[[三疊紀|三疊紀]]早期滅絕。化石發現於[[北美洲|北美洲]]、[[東歐|東歐]]、[[亞洲|亞洲]]與[[澳洲|澳洲]]<ref name="pruitt">{{cite journal | last1 = Tapanila | first1 = L. | last2 = Pruitt | first2 = J. | title = Unravelling species concepts for the ''Helicoprion'' tooth whorl | journal = Journal of Paleontology | volume = 87 | issue = 6 | date = 2013 | doi = 10.1666/12-156 | url = http://geology.isu.edu/Papers/TapanilaPruitt2013.pdf | access-date = 2019-01-03 | archive-date = 2016-06-01 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160601224755/http://geology.isu.edu/Papers/TapanilaPruitt2013.pdf | dead-url = no }}</ref>。旋齒鯊現存關係親緣最相近的物種為[[銀鮫|銀鮫]]<ref name="Tapanila_2013">{{cite journal |author1=Tapanila L. |author2=Pruitt J. |author3=Pradel A. |author4=Wilga C. |author5=Ramsay J. |author6=Schlader R. |author7=Didier D. |title =Jaws for a spiral-tooth whorl: CT images reveal novel adaptation and phylogeny in fossil Helicoprion |journal=Biology Letters |volume =9 |issue =2 |pages =20130057 |year  =2013 |doi  =10.1098/rsbl.2013.0057 |pmid=23445952 |pmc=3639784}}</ref>。

==名称==
Helico源自希臘語「螺旋狀」，Prion則源自「鋸」，組合起來意即「螺旋鋸」。因其下颌上长着排列成螺旋状的牙齿而得名。

==发现==
旋齒鯊在1899年由俄羅斯古生物學家[[亞歷山大·卡爾賓斯基|亞歷山大·卡爾賓斯基]]在[[烏拉爾山脈|烏拉爾山脈]]首次發現。

==描述==
[[File:Helicoprion_as_chimeroid.jpg|thumb]] 
在 2011 年，在[[美國|美國]][[愛達荷州|愛達荷州]]磷酸鹽地層發現了長 {{convert|45|cm|abbr=on}} 的旋齒鯊螺旋齒化石。和其他旋齒鯊的樣本比較後評估，旋齒鯊體長可達 {{convert|10|m|abbr=on}}。在 1980 年（但直到 2013 年才公開）在同一地點其實發現了更大的螺旋齒化石（編號 IMNH 49382）。雖然不完整但是長度可以超過 {{convert|60|cm|abbr=on}}，由此估計該旋齒鯊個體的全長可能超過 {{convert|12|m|abbr=on}}，為目前所知最大的尤金齒目物種<ref name="eartharchives.org">{{cite web|url=http://www.eartharchives.org/articles/buzzsaw-toothed-leviathans-cruised-the-ancient-seas/|title=Buzzsaw-toothed leviathans cruised the ancient seas|author=|date=|website=eartharchives.org|accessdate=2019-01-04|archive-date=2019-05-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190504094647/http://www.eartharchives.org/articles/buzzsaw-toothed-leviathans-cruised-the-ancient-seas/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

